# PulseX Environment Configuration

## Development (.env)

```bash
# Django Settings
DEBUG=True
SECRET_KEY=dev-secret-key-change-in-production
DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=pulsex.settings

# Database
MONGODB_URL=mongodb://localhost:27017/pulsex

# Cache
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379/0

# Authentication
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Notifications
FCM_SERVER_KEY=your-fcm-server-key

# CORS
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=http://localhost:3000,http://127.0.0.1:3000

# Hosts
ALLOWED_HOSTS=localhost,127.0.0.1
```

## Production (.env.prod)

```bash
# Django Settings
DEBUG=False
SECRET_KEY=your-production-secret-key
DJANGO_SETTINGS_MODULE=pulsex.settings

# Database
MONGODB_URL=mongodb+srv://username:password@cluster.mongodb.net/pulsex?retryWrites=true&w=majority

# Cache
REDIS_URL=redis://your-redis-instance:6379/0

# Authentication
GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your-prod-google-client-id.apps.googleusercontent.com

# Notifications
FCM_SERVER_KEY=your-prod-fcm-server-key

# CORS
CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS=https://yourdomain.com,https://www.yourdomain.com

# Hosts
ALLOWED_HOSTS=yourdomain.com,www.yourdomain.com,api.yourdomain.com

# SSL/HTTPS
SECURE_SSL_REDIRECT=True
SESSION_COOKIE_SECURE=True
CSRF_COOKIE_SECURE=True
```

## Environment Variables Reference

| Variable | Description | Required | Default |
|----------|-------------|----------|---------|
| DEBUG | Enable Django debug mode | No | False |
| SECRET_KEY | Django secret key | Yes | None |
| MONGODB_URL | MongoDB connection string | Yes | None |
| REDIS_URL | Redis connection string | Yes | None |
| GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID | Google OAuth client ID | Yes | None |
| FCM_SERVER_KEY | Firebase Cloud Messaging server key | Yes | None |
| CORS_ALLOWED_ORIGINS | Allowed CORS origins (comma-separated) | No | localhost |
| ALLOWED_HOSTS | Allowed Django hosts (comma-separated) | No | localhost |